Game.....: Mat Hoffman's Pro BMX
Origin...: USA - NTSC
Released.: September 13th, 2001
Ripped.......: FMV Downsampled

Mat Hoffman's Pro BMX delivers the most cutting edge and authentic freestyle BMX gaming experience ever. Players can ride like Mat Hoffman, the most recognized name in BMX, or on of seven top pros and perform hundreds of freestyle tricks in a variety of realistic vert, street and dirt courses. 

The game also features multiple modes of play including single player mode, as well as head-to-head two player modes. In addition, with the BMX course editor, players can build their own custom BMX course with ramps, rails, funboxes and a variety of other obstacles.